    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the high-revving S54 inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. The powertrain is mated to a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive subframe reinforcement and a VANOS bulletproofing kit, ensuring the structural and mechanical integrity of the S54 powerplant. The chassis remains composed thanks to refreshed control arm bushings and Bilstein B6 dampers. While the exterior shows minor stone chips consistent with spirited road use, the throttle response is crisp and the longitudinal dynamics remain sharp. An ideal acquisition for an enthusiast seeking a mechanically sound platform without the premium of a garage queen.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 49
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
