    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained, one-owner premium SUV that perfectly balances luxury with daily utility. The exterior retains a deep, glossy luster, having been primarily garage-kept, though you will find the expected minor stone chips on the front bumper consistent with careful highway driving. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary; the leather seating is free of tears or significant bolster wear, and the climate control and infotainment systems function exactly as they did on day one. Mechanically, this vehicle is sound. I have kept a comprehensive folder of all service records, including a recent full synthetic oil change and a brake pad replacement performed last month. The tires have ample tread remaining, ensuring a smooth and safe ride for the new owner. This car has never been smoked in and has been professionally detailed for this sale. It represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer looking for a reliable, high-end vehicle that has been treated with respect and diligence.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
