    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E92 M3 is a mechanically sound example featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L V8, notable for its individual throttle bodies and 8,400 RPM redline. The powertrain is mated to a 6-speed longitudinal manual transmission and an M Variable Differential Lock, ensuring optimal torque distribution. Recent service includes documented rod bearing replacement and new throttle valve actuators to address common S65 pain points. The suspension retains its sharp response via Electronic Damper Control (EDC), while the subframe and bushings remain tight. This is a driver-spec car with linear power delivery and a chassis tuned for technical precision. Minor aesthetic wear is present, but the drivetrain performance is uncompromising.",
